flavor_text_entries.gold:
It uses different
kinds of cries for
communicating with others of its kind
and for pursuing
its prey.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
To corner prey,
they check each
other's location using barks that
only they can
understand.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Around dawn, its
ominous howl
echoes through the area to announce
that this is its
territory.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
HOUNDOUR hunt as a coordinated pack.
They communicate with each other using
a variety of cries to corner their prey. This POKéMON’s remarkable teamwork is
unparalleled.
